    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Caribbean-style fish</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato chips</strong>, <strong>chilli-lime mushy peas</strong> and<strong> lime mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!!</p>",
